  82,5,"ad iéeô yiman ayen d ibbwi, akked wayen iooa"
  82,6,"A yamdan, d acu k i$uôôen, $ef Mass ik Ukyis"
  82,7,"ik Ixelqen, ik Imesslen, ik Iwezznen"
  82,8,Ifka yak udem i aS iwulmen
  82,9,Xaîi! Teskiddibem ddin
  82,10,Ni$ $urwen imêaraben
  82,11,D imura ukyisen
  82,12,èôan ayen txeddmem
  82,13,"Ih, di ssaâd, ara ilin iâaôdiyen"
  82,14,"Ih, di tmessi, ara ilin ucmiten"
  82,15,"A p kecmen, ass iqeîîiyen"
  82,16,"Tuff$a segs, ur zmiren"
