  82,18,"Ih! Anwa ara k imlen, d acu t wass iqeîîiyen"
  82,19,"D ass ideg yiwen ur izmir ad ifukk yiwen, s wacemma. Assen, lameô i Öebbi"
  83,1,"Imed$al, a nnegr nnsen"
  83,2,"Wid, mara d ktilen ar medden, pêeppimen taceôt"
  83,3,"Wanag, nitni, mara ktilen ne$ wezznen, ssenqasen"
  83,4,"Wigi, day ur uminen ar aten id ssekren"
  83,5,ass ameqwôaêan
  83,6,"Ass ideg ara bedden medden, zdat Mass imavalen"
  83,7,"Xaîi! War ccekk, imcumen, di Siooin ara ppujerrden"
  83,8,"Siooin, w ara k t imlen"
  83,9,D tazmamt ipwanesxen
  83,10,"Assen, a nnegr inekkaôen"
  83,11,Wid iskiddiben ass iqeîîiyen
  83,12,"I t inekkôen, siwa amâaûi amednub"
  83,13,"Isekniyen nne£, ma $ôan as ten, yini: \"d tiêkayin imezwura"
  83,14,Xaîi! Maca dubben wulawen nnsen seg wayen kesben
  83,15,"Xaîi! Assen, war ccekk, ad êêurrmen i Mass nnsen"
  83,16,"Sinna, deg u$ud ara ô$en"
  83,17,"Sinna, ad pwanecden: \"atan wacu tnekkôem"
  83,18,"Xaîi! S tidep, ar di Âiliyun, ayen ippujerden i iâaôviyen"
  83,19,"Âiliyun, anwa ara k t imlen"
  83,20,D tazmamt ipwanesxen
  83,21,Inagan is d iqôiben
  83,22,"Di ssaâd ara ilin, war ccekk, iâaôviyen"
  83,23,"F imîeôêen, ssikiden"
  83,24,"A pwaliv deg udmawen nnsen, ticci isaâdiyen"
  83,25,Tissit nnsen d lfayeq ipwacemâen
  83,26,"cmaâ ines d lmesk, f ayagi ad mêizwiren wid ippemêizwiren"
  83,27,"Aman n Tasmin, ad as xelîen"
  83,28,D tala ideg tessen iqôiben
  83,29,"Ih, wid ibe$wven llan ppavûan deg wid iumnen"
  83,30,Ppem$emmazen mara ten mmagren
  83,31,"Mi zzin ar twaculin nnsen, tezzin, ppuraren"
  83,32,"Mara ten walin, ad inin: \"s tidep, wigi nnetlafen"
  83,33,"Ur d pwaznen ara $uôsen, a ten âassen"
  83,34,"Assa, d wid iumnen i ippavûan deg ijehliyen"
  83,35,"£ef imîeôêen, ssikiden"
  83,36,"ma $elten ijehliyen, tirect igiten nnsen"